# demand_tc_witness -- the oracle's input batches (the SAME edge stream the
# driver sends). The oracle evaluates the plain (undemanded) program, so its
# reachable_from rows are the FULL closure -- the answer-identity referee
# for the demand-ON driver's per-key answers.
#
# Batch 1: chain 1->2->3->4 plus the detached 7->8.
batch
+ edge_2 1 2
+ edge_2 2 3
+ edge_2 3 4
+ edge_2 7 8
end

# Batch 2: close the cycle 4->1 and bridge the components 4->7.
batch
+ edge_2 4 1
+ edge_2 4 7
end
